<td width="422" valign="top">
<p style="color: #c90431; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 22px; margin-top: 6px; margin-bottom: 6px;">Our whole team welcomes you!</p>
<p style="margin-top: 10px;"><img src="http://tonyblake.com/TESTsites/honeywell_email/images/HWredline.jpg" alt="" width="650" height="2" /></p>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 4px;">We&rsquo;re the Honeywell Customer Experience Team, a 4 person group specifically created to help improve customer satisfaction while we build loyalty and sales.</p>
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="650">
<tbody>
<tr valign="top">
<td width="179">
<p style="margin-top: 4px;"><img src="http://www.tonyblake.com/TESTsites/honeywell_email/images/Round_Inset_Plane.jpg" alt="" width="160" height="160" /></p>
</td>
<td width="471">
<p style="color: #c90431; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; margin-top: 6px; margin-bottom: 6px;">How will we know we&rsquo;re all doing a good job?</p>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 4px;">Measuring the &ldquo;experience&rdquo; a customer has when they&rsquo;re interacting with us is hard to do. Fortunately, several of our biggest customers do the measuring for us.</p>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 4px;"><strong>GE</strong>, <strong>Airbu</strong><strong>s</strong>, and <strong>Boeing</strong> go to their airline customers with surveys to ask them directly. They rate Honeywell and several other suppliers in areas including delivery, reliability, communication, customer support, and quality.</p>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 4px;">Recently, the ratings haven&rsquo;t been kind. In fact, Honeywell was ranked in the bottom third by Airbus customers, dead last by Boeing, and our GE scores are trending downward.</p>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 4px;">But working together, your team and ours, we&rsquo;re going to turn those numbers around.</p>
<p style="color: #c90431; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; margin-top: 6px; margin-bottom: 6px;">Here&rsquo;s how we&rsquo;ll start to turn the arrows to point in the right direction.</p>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 4px;">Through their answers to the surveys, Honeywell customers said they want us to do an exceptional job at providing them with three things: customer support, ease of delivery, and quick and effective communication.</p>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 4px;"><strong>In our next email, we&rsquo;ll go into depth about what these categories entail, and how Honeywell can achieve excellence in each of them.</strong> And we&rsquo;ll follow up with a third email about how you personally can put all these good intentions into action as you deal effectively with a less-than-happy customer.</p>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 4px;">So, look for  the next email. And let us hear from you with problems or ideas to solve them.</p>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 4px;">The Honeywell Customer Experience Team is on your team.</p>
<p style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;"><img src="http://tonyblake.com/TESTsites/honeywell_email/images/HWgrayline.jpg" alt="" width="650" height="2" /></p>
